Name:        	ppx_shell
Version:     	0.0.1
Synopsis:    	OCaml language extension for shell scripting
Authors:     	Evan Sebastian
License:     	MIT
Plugins:     	META (0.4)
OCamlVersion:	>= 4.02
BuildTools:     ocamlbuild

PreInstallCommand:   $ocamlfind install ppx_shell lib/META
PreUninstallCommand: $ocamlfind remove ppx_shell

Executable ppx_shell
  Path:           lib
  BuildDepends:   Unix, compiler-libs.common, ppx_tools.metaquot
  MainIs:         ppx_shell.ml
  CompiledObject: best

Test test_ppx_shell
  Command:        ocamlbuild -I lib -package oUnit -cflags '-ppx $ppx_shell' test/test_ppx_shell.byte
  TestTools:      ppx_getenv

